
sequenceDiagram
    participant Driver
    participant SteerWheel
    participant DAE
    participant Direction
    participant Wheel

    Note over Driver,Wheel: Steering Flow (Association Chain)
    Driver->>SteerWheel: turn(p_angle)
    SteerWheel->>DAE: use(p_angle)
    DAE->>Direction: turn(p_angle)
    Note over Direction,Wheel: Direction controls 2 front wheels
    Direction->>Wheel: adjust angle
    Wheel-->>Driver: Car turns